ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMERS FOR CRYPTOCURRENCY MINING:

1. USER CONSENT REQUIRED
   This software MUST only be used with explicit consent of the device owner.
   Unauthorized mining constitutes malware/cryptojacking and is illegal.

2. JURISDICTION COMPLIANCE
   Cryptocurrency mining laws vary by country/region. Users are responsible
   for ensuring compliance with local regulations.

3. PLATFORM POLICIES
   - Google Play Store: Prohibits on-device mining apps
   - Apple App Store: Prohibits cryptocurrency mining
   - Microsoft Store: May restrict mining applications
   Distribution through official stores is likely to be rejected.

4. HARDWARE CONSIDERATIONS
   - Extended mining causes battery drain and heat generation
   - May reduce device lifespan due to thermal stress
   - Users assume all hardware warranty risks

5. ENERGY CONSUMPTION
   Mining consumes significant electrical power. Users are responsible for
   associated costs and environmental impact.

6. SECURITY RISKS
   - Wallet keys must be backed up securely
   - Loss of keys = loss of funds (unrecoverable)
   - Use official pool endpoints only

7. NO FINANCIAL ADVICE
   This software is for educational/technical purposes. Authors provide no
   financial advice or profit guarantees.

8. THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
   - XMRig: GPL-3.0 License (https://github.com/xmrig/xmrig)
   - Monero: BSD-3-Clause License
   Users must comply with all third-party licenses.

